data.description: A truly unique and cozy cottage that “plays larger than it looks” thanks to a 4-car driveway, full-length covered front porch, and large, tree-shaded screen room. This original Ocean Pines home is adorned with beautiful tile features, hardwood floors, skylights, and builder accents. First floor has three bedrooms, including primary BR with bath, for one-story living. Additional bedroom upstairs with full bath for the kids or guests. Updates include stainless kitchen appliances, recent roof, new sewer piping, and crawl space encapsulation with sump pump. Heated garage could convert to added family space. Looking for your beach get-away? Well, this is the one!
